---
import SummaryTable from '../../../components/SummaryTable.astro';
import DataTable from '../../../components/DataTable.astro';
import CompareMatrix from '../../../components/CompareMatrix.astro';
import StatGrid from '../../../components/StatGrid.astro';
---

  <section class="component-group" id="group-tables">
    <header class="component-group__header">
      <h2>Bảng &amp; số liệu tĩnh</h2>
      <p>Tóm tắt hàng, bảng so sánh, ma trận tính năng và thẻ metric.</p>
    </header>

  {/* ─────── SummaryTable ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="summarytable">
    <h3>SummaryTable</h3>
    <div class="example-render">
      <SummaryTable
        rows={[
          { id: 'A.1', title: '<a href="#">Kỹ thuật X</a>', chipLabel: 'Loop', chipVariant: 'green' },
          { id: 'A.2', title: '<a href="#">Kỹ thuật Y</a>', chipLabel: 'Context', chipVariant: 'amber' },
          { id: 'B.1', title: '<a href="#">Kỹ thuật Z</a>', chipLabel: 'UNIQUE', chipVariant: 'unique' },
        ]}
      />
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<SummaryTable
  headers={['ID', 'Kỹ thuật', 'Theme']}
  rows={[
    { id: 'A.1', title: '<a href="#t1">...</a>', chipLabel: 'Loop', chipVariant: 'green' },
  ]}
/>`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  {/* ─────── DataTable ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="datatable">
    <h3>DataTable</h3>
    <div class="example-render">
      <DataTable
        variant="compare"
        richCells
        headers={['Aspect', 'Project A', 'Project B']}
        rows={[
          ['Language', '<code>TypeScript</code>', '<code>Python</code>'],
          ['Multi-agent', 'Task tool', '<strong>Subprocess swarm</strong>'],
        ]}
      />
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<DataTable
  variant="compare"
  richCells
  headers={['Aspect', 'A', 'B']}
  rows={[
    ['Language', '<code>TS</code>', '<code>Python</code>'],
  ]}
/>`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  {/* ─────── CompareMatrix ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="comparematrix">
    <h3>CompareMatrix</h3>
    <p>Feature matrix với ✓/✗/~ color-coded. Đẹp hơn DataTable khi so sánh feature support. Values: <code>'yes'</code> | <code>'no'</code> | <code>'partial'</code> | <code>'na'</code> | string tùy ý.</p>
    <div class="example-render">
      <CompareMatrix
        features={['Text import', 'Template vars', 'Type-safe schema', 'A/B test prompt']}
        subjects={['opencode', 'Claude Code', 'Aider', 'OpenHarness']}
        cells={[
          [{value:'yes'}, {value:'no'}, {value:'no'}, {value:'no'}],
          [{value:'yes'}, {value:'partial', note:'f-string'}, {value:'no'}, {value:'partial', note:'f-string'}],
          [{value:'yes'}, {value:'yes'}, {value:'no'}, {value:'no'}],
          [{value:'yes'}, {value:'partial'}, {value:'no'}, {value:'no'}],
        ]}
        caption="So sánh quản lý tool description giữa các harness"
      />
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<CompareMatrix
  features={['Feature A', 'Feature B']}
  subjects={['Tool 1', 'Tool 2']}
  cells={[
    [{value:'yes'}, {value:'no'}],
    [{value:'partial', note:'caveat'}, {value:'yes'}],
  ]}
/>`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  {/* ─────── StatGrid ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="statgrid">
    <h3>StatGrid</h3>
    <p>Grid metric cards — big number + label + note tùy chọn. Variants: <code>green</code>, <code>amber</code>, <code>red</code>, <code>purple</code>, <code>cyan</code>. Dùng ở intro section.</p>
    <div class="example-render">
      <StatGrid stats={[
        { value: '28', label: 'Kỹ thuật', note: 'phân tích chi tiết' },
        { value: '6', label: 'Nhóm chủ đề', variant: 'green' },
        { value: '3', label: 'Deep dives', variant: 'cyan' },
        { value: '94%', label: 'Tool coverage', variant: 'amber' },
      ]} columns={4} />
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<StatGrid stats={[
  { value: '28', label: 'Kỹ thuật', note: 'phân tích chi tiết' },
  { value: '6', label: 'Nhóm', variant: 'green' },
  { value: '94%', label: 'Coverage', variant: 'amber' },
]} columns={3} />`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  </section>
